OL,3,C'We know we've more to do': Burnham
OL,4,Cvisits veterans hub with defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Mayor Andy Burnham
OL,8,Fhas said he "knows we have more to do"
OL,9,Fto combat veteran homelessness.
OL,11,FHe joined Defence Secretary John Healy
OL,12,Fat a veterans hub in Wigan, following
OL,13,Fthe announcement of up to #1 million
OL,14,Ffunding for veteran centres across the
OL,15,Fcountry.
OL,17,FBurnham said: "It's crucial that when
OL,18,Fpeople who have served this country
OL,19,Fcome back, we give them everything
OL,20,Fthey need to rebuild their lives.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
