FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776348651
OL,3,C'We know we've more to do': Burnham
OL,4,Cvisits veterans hub with defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FThe former Leigh MP pointed out the
OL,8,Flack of support that was previously
OL,9,Favailable for armed forces returning
OL,10,Ffrom Afghanistan and Iraq during his
OL,11,Ftime in the Commons.
OL,13,FHe said: "Many people fell between the
OL,14,Fcracks. The mental health support just
OL,15,Fwas not good enough and what this
OL,16,Fborough did is it saw that, and
OL,17,Fresponded with this investment."
OL,19,FDean Hook - a veteran and recovering
OL,20,Falcoholic - said the centre is like a
OL,21,Fsecond home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776348651
OL,3,C'We know we've more to do': Burnham
OL,4,Cvisits veterans hub with defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FHe said: "Just because I'm sober... I
OL,8,Fstruggle daily and I can talk to the
OL,9,Fguys and staff here and they're there
OL,10,Ffor me. This place is a comfort
OL,11,Fblanket to me, and that's how I like
OL,12,Fit.
OL,14,F"It's all about support. There's no
OL,15,Fpoint in giving someone a flat, they
OL,16,Fneed to want that support. You've got
OL,17,Fto want to change, but it's having the
OL,18,Fright people at your side who you can
OL,19,Ftalk to.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776348651
OL,3,C'We know we've more to do': Burnham
OL,4,Cvisits veterans hub with defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,F"I struggle with opening up to people
OL,8,Fbecause I think they're taking the
OL,9,Fp**** out of me, and that's why I can
OL,10,Ftalk to people here."
OL,12,FHe said he feels less judged at the
OL,13,Fcentre since most people there can
OL,14,Frelate to what he has been through.
OL,16,FBurnham and Healy spoke to veterans at
OL,17,Fthe hub - The Armed Forces Community
OL,18,FHQ - which will now receive funding
OL,19,Ffrom the government.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
