PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776348651
OL,3,C'We know we've more to do': Burnham
OL,4,Cvisits veterans hub with defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FThe visit marked the Mayor's second
OL,8,Fmeeting with a cabinet minister this
OL,9,Fweek, following questions about his
OL,10,Frelationship with Number 10 after he
OL,11,Fwas denied permission to run for
OL,12,Fparliament in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,13,Felection in February 2026.
OL,15,FBurnham said he will always considers
OL,16,Fhimself a Labour team player: "I put
OL,17,Fmyself forward, it didn't work, and
OL,18,FI've gone back to my job as Mayor of
OL,19,FGreater Manchester."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776348651
OL,3,C'We know we've more to do': Burnham
OL,4,Cvisits veterans hub with defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FHe said: "I'm proud that the defence
OL,8,Fsecretary is here in Wigan this
OL,9,Fmorning to see this incredible armed
OL,10,Fforces community hub that's been
OL,11,Fcreated. Wigan council deserve great
OL,12,Fcredit for bringing this facility into
OL,13,Fbeing.
OL,15,F"For me to be back as a former Wigan
OL,16,Fborough MP to see what it's become is
OL,17,Ftruly inspiring. This is one of the
OL,18,Fbest facilities for supporting our
OL,19,Farmed forces anywhere in the country."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776348651
OL,3,C'We know we've more to do': Burnham
OL,4,Cvisits veterans hub with defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FThe Wigan veterans hub will be a part
OL,8,Fof the UK's first ever network of
OL,9,Fgovernment backed veteran support
OL,10,Fcentres. The network is part of VALOUR
OL,11,F- a programme that the government says
OL,12,Fwill "tackle the current fragmented
OL,13,Fnature of accessing support."
OL,15,FSpeaking at the hub, Healy said: "In
OL,16,Fthis country for too long we have
OL,17,Foften let our veterans down. They have
OL,18,Fserved the country and when they have
OL,19,Fneeded support it hasn't been there
OL,20,Ffor them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776348651
OL,3,C'We know we've more to do': Burnham
OL,4,Cvisits veterans hub with defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,F"This centre is a great example of
OL,8,Fwhen you've got a good local
OL,9,Forganisation, backed by a good city
OL,10,Fmayor, and now also by central
OL,11,Fgovernment, we can put in place a
OL,12,Fsingle point of service housing,
OL,13,Femployment, training, and welfare
OL,14,Fbenefits.
OL,16,F"If people need somewhere to turn,
OL,17,Fthey've got one place to come and this
OL,18,Fis a model that I want see replicated
OL,19,Ffrom Manchester around other parts of
OL,20,Fthe country."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776348651
OL,3,C'We know we've more to do': Burnham
OL,4,Cvisits veterans hub with defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FConservative Leader Kemi Badenoch has
OL,8,Fbeen amongst many who are calling for
OL,9,Fanswers about whether the government
OL,10,Fwill need to decrease the welfare bill
OL,11,Fin order to increase defence spending.
OL,13,FFormer NATO chief Lord George
OL,14,FRobertson has warned of "corrosive
OL,15,Fcomplacency" from Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,16,Fgovernment, claiming the UK is
OL,17,Funderprepared for war due to the "ever-
OL,18,Fexpanding welfare budget".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776348651
OL,3,C'We know we've more to do': Burnham
OL,4,Cvisits veterans hub with defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FHealy said reforms are being made to
OL,8,Fthe welfare state - that was "broken
OL,9,Fby the last government", and claimed
OL,10,FLabour are also "increasing defence
OL,11,Fspending by record amounts".
OL,13,FAndy Burnham said: "I think we've got
OL,14,Fto face the reality of the world we
OL,15,Fare in. We're going to have to invest
OL,16,Fmore in our security and we have to
OL,17,Ffind a way as a country to do that,
OL,18,Fand I know the Prime Minister and the
OL,19,Fgovernment do know that.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776348651
OL,3,C'We know we've more to do': Burnham
OL,4,Cvisits veterans hub with defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,F"It's not about cut one area to
OL,8,Fprioritise another, this has just got
OL,9,Fto be done, and we will do our part in
OL,10,FGreater Manchester in supporting the
OL,11,Fgovernment in doing that."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
